msgid "tānassu kukkuṭiyā sammā adhisayitāni, sammā pariseditāni, sammā paribhāvitāni. "
msgstr "properly sat on them to keep them warm and incubated. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.101:5.9"
msgid "Evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhāvanānuyogaṃ anuyuttassa bhikkhuno viharato kiñcāpi na evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya: "
msgstr "In the same way, when a mendicant is committed to development, they might not wish: "

