msgid "‘aho vata me anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimucceyyā’ti, atha khvassa anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuccati. "
msgstr "‘If only my mind was freed from the defilements by not grasping!’ Even so, their mind is freed from defilements by not grasping. "

msgctxt "sn22.101:5.11"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn22.101:5.12"
